{"tid":2181410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警告美軍？解放軍邀美方參觀U-2偵察機殘骸","createTime":"2020-08-30T14:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T07:23:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":162,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"c08b449a12b3324c124fa8a84c64095cddeb4834","tid":2181410,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2735000/2739015/0830_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2735000%2F2739015%2F0830_1024.jpg&h=458829e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美地緣角力升級，解放軍近期密集公布在北海、黃海、渤海、南海軍演，美國U-2高空偵察機則一度飛入渤海中國主張的「禁飛區」，位於北京的中國人民革命軍事博物館對此發文稱，「軍博請你來參觀U-2殘骸」，有警告美方意味。<br />\n<br />\n中國人民革命軍事博物館（簡稱軍博）屬中央軍委政治工作部旗下，該館在微博指出，歷史上中國曾多次擊落U-2高空偵察機，1962年9月9日，中國空軍地空飛彈部隊在江西南昌埋伏，首次擊落U-2高空偵察機，後來共擊落5架，成為全球擊落此機型最多的國家，飛機殘骸現在陳列於中國人民革命軍事博物館地下一層兵器大廳。<br />\n<br />\n軍博展覽U-2殘骸 屬中華民國軍隊而非美軍<br />\n<br />\n文內也介紹了60年代U-2高空偵察機的基本數據，飛行高度為27000米，最大平飛速度每小時810公里，續航時間8小時，有效偵查高度5000米至15000米，能拍出地面景物清晰圖像，相當於巨型空中間諜軍團。<br />\n<br />\n但值得注意是，解放軍歷史上擊落的U-2偵察機，不是屬於美軍，而是屬於台灣一方的。<br />\n<br />\n文末警告，中國58年前能打下U-2高空偵察機，58年後能打下任何侵入中國的戰機：<br />\n<br />\n前天闖入中國禁飛區的美國飛行員，有空帶上身份證，掃二維碼，來中國人民革命軍事博物館，參觀一下U-2高空偵察機的殘骸。我們會講給你聽，那是我們半個多世紀前打下來的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2739015/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%EF%BC%9F%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E9%82%80%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%83%E8%A7%80U-2%E5%81%B5%E5%AF%9F%E6%A9%9F%E6%AE%98%E9%AA%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2739015%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%258A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25EF%25BC%259F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%2582%2580%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25A7%2580U-2%25E5%2581%25B5%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25AE%2598%25E9%25AA%25B8&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoEYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=3f06b517\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2739015/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%EF%BC%9F%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E9%82%80%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%83%E8%A7%80U-2%E5%81%B5%E5%AF%9F%E6%A9%9F%E6%AE%98%E9%AA%B8</a>"},{"pid":"111869fb53bea60c9d857865a51130ec718afd48","tid":2181410,"uid":108201,"like":249,"dislike":13,"score":236,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P67KJan.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP67KJan.gif&h=2ec23dd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77e6652c6bd2917b14f7e4e4b9de834d49101122","tid":2181410,"uid":8776,"like":221,"dislike":3,"score":218,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXgoegZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXgoegZ.png&h=0ded039d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全部台仔既<br />\n美軍:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e07f38ff0f501ccf44b8dbb7f08fd4dbd0983c0","tid":2181410,"uid":59461,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"美國:上次楊潔遞黎夏威夷我未帶佢參觀珍珠港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c60937974ed3498e7e28a770364e8667cf26666","tid":2181410,"uid":25424,"like":159,"dislike":2,"score":157,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"U2第一日俾人射落嚟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺明睇你唔起，唔夠膽射，先再出U2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中国人個腦真係on99，笑緊你都唔知，仲要俾多個位人哋笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad